{"id": 2307, "genre": 1001, "title": "【好奇心xFresh】为了不负好春光，你最近都践行了哪些健康活力的生活方式？", "description": "春风一吹想起谁？活力满满才不后悔", "record_count": 8425, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 0, "image": "img/paper/paper_show/201804261207012NslUnPh5W6B1yGw.jpeg", "page_style": 0, "category": 3, "column": 2, "type": "paper", "date": "2018-04-27T03:00:00Z", "options": [{"id": 278786, "content": "运动", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1308841}, {"id": 278531, "content": "戒烟", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 988350}, {"id": 278532, "content": "不加班?", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 110302}, {"id": 278788, "content": "运动，少油炸", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1322331}, {"id": 279300, "content": "尽量出门走走", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1307531}, {"id": 278540, "content": "更多的使用手机，这样就可以多躺着，保护腰", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1329020}, {"id": 278797, "content": "√water 多喝水\n√fruit  多吃喜欢的水果\n睡前做各种小保健操。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1329252}, {"id": 282125, "content": "就算最后知道是白费力，也要做。每天早上起来别人都还在睡的时候，我想的是就算效率低也要把早起的习惯保持下去。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1290009}, {"id": 278286, "content": "油多的菜很少选择了，不喝奶茶了，喜欢多吃蔬菜、水果、酸奶", "image": null, "praise_count": 932, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 684014}, {"id": 282126, "content": "三个月一周三到四次，15到20公里不停歇长跑，瘦了十斤。坚持晚餐吃少接近两年，体重维持不变！", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 970221}, {"id": 278287, "content": "开始骑摩托！不能更开心！", "image": null, "praise_count": 84, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1328155}, {"id": 278288, "content": "运动后吃水果、酸奶，感受围度一点一点掉下去，觉得生活真的幸福且积极", "image": null, "praise_count": 99, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 771439}, {"id": 278800, "content": "哭。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1178586}, {"id": 282128, "content": "坚持喜欢你", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1346120}, {"id": 278289, "content": "睡前跑步", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 419664}, {"id": 283921, "content": "跑步、吃水果、摄影", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 940627}, {"id": 278290, "content": " 睡前喝牛奶，2公里内尽量走路", "image": null, "praise_count": 94, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 991016}, {"id": 278291, "content": "晚上跑跑步，锻炼一下", "image": null, "praise_count": 347, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1327159}, {"id": 278293, "content": "每天跑步，早睡早起", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 639703}, {"id": 278294, "content": "不是泡椒凤爪了", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1327120}, {"id": 278295, "content": "健身+控制饮食", "image": null, "praise_count": 10, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 966594}, {"id": 278807, "content": "坚持去健身房，学习一两个自己喜欢的乐器，十一点半之前睡觉（这个正在改进），有空了就看东方时空，炒菜不放辣椒，少吃油腻的东西，定期体检，多喝茶（不是奶茶，是正儿八经的茶叶）", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1330479}, {"id": 278296, "content": "多看书，不熬夜，不赖床，早起吃早餐。", "image": null, "praise_count": 649, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1022107}, {"id": 278297, "content": "锻炼身体", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1182706}, {"id": 278809, "content": "不吃加辣的食物。", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1330516}, {"id": 278299, "content": "晚上9年睡觉。。", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 258307}, {"id": 278300, "content": "起个大早去吃brunch！～～", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1156827}, {"id": 278812, "content": "早睡早起", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 575362}, {"id": 278301, "content": "早起锻炼身体", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1151252}, {"id": 278302, "content": "不熬夜，多喝水！", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1207126}, {"id": 282142, "content": "健身＋控制饮食", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1346189}, {"id": 278303, "content": "早睡不吃鸡", "image": null, "praise_count": 6, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 950816}, {"id": 278048, "content": "早睡不一定，早起要争取，伴随清早的阳光，边敷面膜边准备健康早餐", "image": null, "praise_count": 1406, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 688713}, {"id": 278304, "content": "早睡早起，11点一定睡觉", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1208858}, {"id": 278049, "content": "护肤品开始转用天然成分更多的，包装也要看得见的透亮，给自己一个好心情 ", "image": null, "praise_count": 573, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 688713}, {"id": 278305, "content": "减少油盐调味品的摄入 清淡饮食 水果蔬菜肉类均衡饮食 保持愉悦心情 早睡早起 利用碎片化时间 养成阅读学习的好习惯 ", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1328182}, {"id": 278050, "content": "克制奶茶和咖啡，下午茶选择新鲜的果汁，柠檬啦，甜橙啦，补充维他命", "image": null, "praise_count": 728, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 688713}, {"id": 278306, "content": "管住嘴迈开腿，放下手机佛系人生", "image": null, "praise_count": 155, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1107204}, {"id": 278818, "content": "早起跑步，晚做瑜伽，按时三餐", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1286483}, {"id": 282146, "content": "报一堂英语口语课，并坚持下去。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1344368}, {"id": 278051, "content": "天气暖了，没有借口不出去跑步举铁了，BodyPump，BodyCombat走起", "image": null, "praise_count": 207, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 688713}, {"id": 278307, "content": "天天喊着要早睡", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1277082}, {"id": 278052, "content": "外卖从每周5次减到每周3次，多出去溜达觅食", "image": null, "praise_count": 78, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 688713}, {"id": 278308, "content": "临近大学毕业，看电影，爬山，写随笔", "image": null, "praise_count": 5, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1328181}, {"id": 278309, "content": "7点前醒来精神还不错就散步半小时，困的话继续休息。\n\n每天保持1小时阅读\n\n晚上9:30—10:30跑步+散步   边听音乐\n\n早餐前一杯奶或者水   中饭后一杯蜂蜜水\n下午6点一杯水\n675\n睡觉前回忆背的专业书，5个仰卧起坐", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1315875}, {"id": 286245, "content": "早睡。用好的护肤品。多喝水多吃水果多运动。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1216513}, {"id": 278310, "content": "坚持11点前入睡，坚持吃早餐，尽量不喝饮料，实在想喝只喝鲜榨，水果蔬菜吃当季", "image": null, "praise_count": 5, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1212038}, {"id": 278823, "content": "减肥真理：管住嘴，迈开腿", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1292662}, {"id": 278312, "content": "早睡早起 健康饮食～饭后散步～", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1176704}, {"id": 278313, "content": "早睡早起，不晚睡不熬夜", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1107203}]}